OL,3,CA new public broadcaster should be
OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,FA new public service broadcaster
OL,7,Fshould be considered in the event of a
OL,8,Funited Ireland, researchers have said.
OL,10,FSuch a new model would involve hubs in
OL,11,F10 areas across the island and draw on
OL,12,Fthe assets, infrastructure and people
OL,13,Fof RTE and BBC Northern Ireland, the
OL,14,Fresearcher from Ulster University and
OL,15,FDCU argued.
OL,17,FAn alternative media provision also
OL,18,Fhad merit, the joint report said,
OL,19,Fwhere an all-island platform ` eg, an
OL,20,FiPlayer Ireland ` could be established.
