OL,3,CA new public broadcaster should be
OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,FThe report, launched on Wednesday,
OL,7,Fexamined whether BBC Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fwould continue, whether RTE would take
OL,9,Fover, or if a new body should be set
OL,10,Fup in the event of a united Ireland.
OL,12,FThe authors concluded that replicating
OL,13,Fthe RTE/BBC funding structure would
OL,14,Fcause difficulties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
