OL,3,CA new public broadcaster should be
OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,F"We argue that achieving buy-in and
OL,7,Fsupport from the two main communities
OL,8,Fwithin NI will be more easily won if
OL,9,Finstitutions are created afresh,
OL,10,Frather than simply grafting on
OL,11,Fnorthern parts to their southern
OL,12,Fcounterparts," it said.
OL,14,F"Moreover, the persistent governance
OL,15,Fissues that RTE has faced in recent
OL,16,Fyears means that a new start is
OL,17,Fpreferable."
