OL,3,CA new public broadcaster should be
OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,FIt said that maintaining the status
OL,7,Fquo was "most likely a non-starter",
OL,8,Fbecause the region of Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fwould be outside the UK TV Licence
OL,10,Fframework in a reunified Ireland.
OL,12,FIt said that TV licences that fund the
OL,13,FBBC are not levied anywhere outside of
OL,14,Fthe UK, but added that it was also
OL,15,Funlikely that audiences in NI would
OL,16,Flose access to BBC radio and
OL,17,Ftelevision programmes.
