OL,3,CA new public broadcaster should be
OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,FInstead, it said that a new public
OL,7,Fservice media in the event of Irish
OL,8,Funity should be considered,
OL,9,Fprovisionally called Public Media
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FIt said regional coverage would be
OL,13,F"crucial" and suggested 10 regional
OL,14,Fjournalism hubs ` in Belfast, Derry,
OL,15,FEnniskillen, Newry, Athlone, Galway,
OL,16,FLimerick, Dublin, Waterford and Cork `
OL,17,Fthat would cover cultural stories as
OL,18,Fwell as news.
