OL,3,CA new public broadcaster should be
OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,FIt said such a new media organisation
OL,7,Fshould be diverse and "decentralised"
OL,8,Fand based on a sustainable funding
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,FThe report warned of funding issues
OL,12,Fand TV licence fee evasion rates at
OL,13,FRTE and the BBC, as well as political
OL,14,Finterference if direct funding was
OL,15,Fintroduced, and recommended that a new
OL,16,Fmedia group be funded like the Finnish
OL,17,Fpublic media model.
