OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,FThis sees people pay 2.5% of their
OL,7,F"total earned income and capital
OL,8,Fincome" above 14,000 euro, but the
OL,9,Fmaximum payment is 163 euro per year.
OL,11,FThe research, compiled by academics
OL,12,Ffrom Ulster University and Dublin City
OL,13,FUniversity, acknowledges that Irish
OL,14,Freunification is not imminent or
OL,15,Finevitable.
