OL,3,CA new public broadcaster should be
OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,FIt also said that the media sector is
OL,7,Flikely to come further down the list
OL,8,Fof priorities for discussion and
OL,9,Fplanning, after key priorities such as
OL,10,Fhealthcare, taxation, policing and
OL,11,Fsymbols of identity.
OL,13,FAn author of the report, Dr Phil
OL,14,FRamsey from Ulster University, said
OL,15,Fthe research "kickstarts a debate" on
OL,16,Fwhat the future of media might look
OL,17,Flike across Ireland.
OL,26,@wD@NOUwD@bO]
