OL,3,CA new public broadcaster should be
OL,4,Cconsidered in a united Ireland ` report
OL,6,F"This is the beginning of a
OL,7,Fconversation, and we want interested
OL,8,Fparties to have their say on the
OL,9,Frecommendations."
OL,11,FDr Dawn Wheatley from Dublin City
OL,12,FUniversity, said: "It is impossible to
OL,13,Fsay with certainty what might happen
OL,14,Fto public media should the
OL,15,Freunification of Ireland ever occur.
OL,17,F"But in this report we suggest that
OL,18,Fpublic broadcasters play a vital role
OL,19,Fwithin democracies, and so they should
OL,20,Fnot be overlooked in wider debates."
